{"tid":99042,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[處境解難]  新年處境題","createTime":"2017-01-29T01:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T02:32:50.000Z","uid":77636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"890f5bcc6df3ed4333c1e43d73bef47283399506","tid":99042,"uid":77636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T01:25:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，見今個農曆新年，有4日假放，又唔洗去拜年，自自然然就鎖起房門，預備射個仔埋牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n我用左轉身射個3分波時間，好快就決定好，新一年要好好寵幸一下三上悠亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。好快就進入大直路，我不斷快馬加鞭，悠亞都已經進入狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。點知，班仆街親戚突然上黎拜年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我一於好少理，繼續策騎悠亞，我都就見孩子既未來。但最估唔到係我老豆，老豆以為我又玩緊線上賭場。<br />\n<br />\n佢一路話:衰仔唔好掛住賭錢啦，表弟佢地黎拜年，出黎招呼下人。<br />\n一路拎住條後備匙，開我房門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n我屌佢老味，好死唔死班親戚好似迎賓咁企係我老豆後面，望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n同兩老生活左咁多年，我都唔知佢地一直有後備匙。今次真係比老豆你玩死，我只能講一句佩服!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時，悠亞後勁好凌厲，我一時收制不及，射到成地都係精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n為左緩和緊張氣氛，我:恭喜發財，兒孫滿堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n老豆同親戚: ......<br />\n然後老豆就關埋房門，依家就同親戚出面坐緊，一聲都無出過。<br />\n<br />\n所以我想問，我個笑話真係咁差咩，點解大家靜左咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b95edc1d325b237154047a97215c789d4dc6dc","tid":99042,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T01:27:35.000Z","msg":"有是咁的，但0分"},{"pid":"4ad591481083fff65308641a6317d871492dcf3f","tid":99042,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T01:44:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e768343168727b1a0ecf5d3dc544a242baf09b9b","tid":99042,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:27:42.000Z","msg":"唔好著褲同佢地拜年 佢地見到就會笑架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9679e33a49a2238f764bacfd65054bfc981b9ea","tid":99042,"uid":77636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:32:50.000Z","msg":"開始有笑聲，佢地好似get到個笑點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}